        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks HdS for pebbles of Roman bricks. When he goes over MS [<hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>] again, he will compare smoother ones with those having undergone attrition in gizzards of worms.</p> 
            <p>Has received book [<hi rend="italic">La question du lac</hi>] sent by HdS.</p>
            <p>Also sends photograph taken by Leonard Darwin of CD.</p>
            <p>Requests photograph of HdS to add to his collection.</p>
